# Web project (this repo)

Cloned from `web-motion-starter`. Global orchestration: `~/.cursor/skills/site-builder/SKILL.md`.

## Before editing

1. Read `docs/SITE-BRIEF.md` (fill if empty)
2. Prefer sections from `docs/SECTION-CATALOG.md` — do not rewrite hero/pricing from scratch
3. Brand: `src/lib/theme/brand-palette.css` or `npm run sync:tokens`

## Structure

- `src/components/sections/` — landing blocks
- `src/components/pages/home-page.tsx` — composed landing
- `src/lib/site-config.ts` — `siteFeatures` flags
- `content/site.json` — nav + tagline

## QA before handoff

```bash
npm run qa:all
```

## Deploy

```bash
npm run deploy
```

See `docs/DEPLOY.md`.
